      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The capstone project serves many goals in the nursing course. However, the primary goals are anchored in the need for students to demonstrate theoretical knowledge in solving practice-based issues in various nursing specialties. Check out why it is important to write a nursing capstone project.</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-1">
